{"tid":2142893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會因為留喺屋企嘅時間多左，而多左同屋企人嘈？","createTime":"2020-08-06T17:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T00:46:35.000Z","uid":351978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19d48940419c2823685dc97f9929a45ee788f59b","tid":2142893,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"疫情之前，都話可以成日出街，減少同阿媽嘈嘅機會。但係疫情之後，多左時間留喺屋企，自然同阿媽多咗野講，但多嘢講嘅後果就係嘈交，佢又成日話我嘅生活習慣，又話我夜訓。我越黎越唔想同佢講野，好唔想有衝突，但總係避無可避。大家係咪都有呢個情況出現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cd7b782dc8e12458d3c06c4b73afeefbf1ce39","tid":2142893,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"都唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859de6d032f7856a2a758d87d2078821d8ed1331","tid":2142893,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"扮聽唔到"},{"pid":"764a35cea07a71bf06cff6d9821e17e055814fec","tid":2142893,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8cd7b782dc8e12458d3c06c4b73afeefbf1ce39","tid":2142893,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"都唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:26:09.000Z","msg":"我都想唔講野，平時都已經匿埋喺自己間房唔出客廳，平時食飯都會夾埋啲餸入返自己間房食。但係因為我間房有好多雜物同佢嘅衣櫃，所以佢成日都會借啲意入嚟我間房話拎嘢。我覺得佢好煩，成日監察我嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7086e54e4266ba827fe1f19326bdc9e77349ff20","tid":2142893,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859de6d032f7856a2a758d87d2078821d8ed1331","tid":2142893,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"扮聽唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"我都會，但係佢跟住就會喺客廳大聲咁樣鬧我，製造噪音污染，話我唔肯幫佢拎嘢又剩"},{"pid":"6ea95f0761265a6461f056ee801fef1d288059f1","tid":2142893,"uid":3